name: FloorStyler
overview: The purpose of Floor styler is to provide easy means for quick sketching of floor plans with the help of intuitive user interface! Floor styler is useful in cases in which is needed a basic spatial representation of rooms - something which cannot be easily comprehended only with photos. It can also be used for getting a basic idea if rearangement of the existing furnutire and fixtures is needed. The apparent benefit for owners of real estate websites is that they can attract more visitors with the improved feature of the websites. Floor styler can be easily integrated with existing websites without need for complex and lengthy procedures. Furthermore, it relies on the Adobe Flash technology which guarantees support by all browsers. Floor styler is a software product based on the Adobe Flash technology targeted mainly towards owners of real estate websites. The purpose of Floor styler is to provide easy means for quick sketching of floor plans with the help of intuitive user interface.
